room_title: Escape room "Interstellar" by Key Quest in Tulsa
room_description: You are members of an exploratory team of astronauts at the far reaches of the galaxy on board the spacecraft USS Endeavor. Your team is tasked with finding a planet suitable to sustain human life. You must solve a series of challenges put in place by the central computer system in order to circumvent the security protocols and navigate your way to the escape pod.
